\f0\fs32 \cf0 __SITE_DATA_DIR__
\f1 \
\
Internal variable, const, cannot be changed in !define files.\
\
Contains the path to the local machine data directory on the machine were instl is currently running. Value is usually same as 
\f0 __SITE_CONFIG_DIR__
\f1 .\
\
Note: "Site" in operating system jargon means location on disk that are common to all users yet are local to the machine.\
\
On Windows this will typically be:\
C:\\ProgramData\
\
On Mac:\
/Library/Application Support\
\
Usage:\
\

\f2 \cb2 --- !define\
ACME_SITE_DATA_DIR: $(__SITE_DATA_DIR__)/acme.site.data\
\
--- !index\
SOME_ACME_SOFTWARE:\
	install_sources:\
		- default_data_file.txt\
	install_folders:\
		- $(ACME_SITE_DATA_DIR)\

\f1 \cb1 \
Variable value is set by: \
In main function, by calling appdirs.site_data_dir().\
